<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>Aerospace Engineering Learning Hub</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-bg: #0A0A1A;
      /* Dark space background */
      --section-bg: #141428;
      /* Slightly lighter background */
      --card-bg: #1E1E3A;
      /* Card background */
      --card-hover: #2A2A4A;
      /* Card hover effect */
      --text-primary: #E5E5FF;
      /* Light text color */
      --text-secondary: #A0A0CC;
      /* Muted text color */
      --accent: #7B68EE;
      /* Purple accent */
      --accent-hover: #9370DB;
      /* Lighter purple for hover */
      --highlight: #00BFFF;
      /* Bright blue for highlights */
      --border: #3A3A5A;
      /* Border color */
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--primary-bg);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(50, 50, 100, 0.1) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 26, 0.1) 100%);
    }

    .navbar {
      background: var(--section-bg);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .back-button {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-button:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: var(--section-bg);
      background-image: url('/placeholder.svg?height=400&width=1200');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-blend-mode: overlay;
      position: relative;
    }

    header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(20, 20, 40, 0.7);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    header h1, header p {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.5);
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .topics-grid,
    .specialization-grid,
    .projects-grid,
    .practice-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .topic-card,
    .specialization-card,
    .project-card,
    .practice-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .topic-card:hover,
    .specialization-card:hover,
    .project-card:hover,
    .practice-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--card-hover);
    }

    .topic-title,
    .specialization-title,
    .project-title {
      color: var(--highlight);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .learn-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .learn-btn:hover {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.3);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: var(--section-bg);
      margin-top: 4rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .quote {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .project-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .project-tag {
      background: rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.2);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .features-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .features-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .features-list i {
      color: var(--highlight);
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .resources-section {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .channel-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .channel-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .channel-list i {
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .resource-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      header {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      section {
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .topics-grid,
      .specialization-grid,
      .projects-grid,
      .practice-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="nav-container">
      <a href="#" class="logo">Aerospace Engineering</a>
      <a href="/Engineering/MECH/mech.ejs" class="back-button">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <h1>Aerospace Engineering Specialization</h1>
    <p>Master the fundamentals of aircraft and spacecraft design, propulsion, and systems with comprehensive learning resources.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="specialization-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Specialization Areas</h2>
    <div class="specialization-grid">
  
      <!-- Propulsion Systems -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
          Propulsion Systems
        </div>
        <p>Focus on jet engines, rocket propulsion, and advanced propulsion technologies.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Jet & turbine engines</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Rocket propulsion</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Electric propulsion</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: #00BFFF;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/NASASpaceflightVideos" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> NASA Spaceflight</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/EverydayAstronaut" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Everyday Astronaut</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.aiaa.org/publications/journals" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> AIAA Journals</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Aerodynamics -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-wind"></i>
          Aerodynamics
        </div>
        <p>Study of airflow around aircraft, lift generation, drag reduction, and flight stability.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Computational fluid dynamics</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Wind tunnel testing</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> High-speed aerodynamics</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: #00BFFF;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnEngineering" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Learn Engineering</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/FlightMechanic" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Flight Mechanics</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862342" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Fundamentals of Aerodynamics</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Aerospace Structures -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-cubes"></i>
          Aerospace Structures
        </div>
        <p>Focus on structural design, materials, and analysis for aircraft and spacecraft.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Composite materials</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Structural analysis</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Fatigue & fracture mechanics</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: #00BFFF;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/NASAGoddard" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> NASA Goddard</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/MaterialsScienceandEngineering" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Materials Science</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862350" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Aircraft Structures</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- Projects section -->
  <section class="projects-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Industry Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-satellite"></i>
          CubeSat Development
        </div>
        <p>Design and build small satellites for research, Earth observation, and technology demonstration.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Orbital Mechanics</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Payload Integration</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Power Systems</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/smallsat-institute/cubesat-101/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Research</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-plane"></i>
          Urban Air Mobility
        </div>
        <p>Develop electric vertical takeoff and landing (eVTOL) aircraft for urban transportation.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Electric Propulsion</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Flight Control</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Noise Reduction</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/aeroresearch/programs/iasp/uam/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Course</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-meteor"></i>
          Hypersonic Vehicle Design
        </div>
        <p>Research and develop vehicles capable of sustained flight at Mach 5+ speeds.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Thermal Protection</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Scramjet Engines</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Aerothermodynamics</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/centers/armstrong/features/X-43A.html" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Tools</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Flight Mechanics & Stability</div>
        <p>Understand the principles of aircraft motion, stability, and control.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.103278" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Propulsion Systems</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of jet engines, rockets, and advanced propulsion technologies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862373" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Aerospace Materials</div>
        <p>Learn about materials selection, properties, and applications in aerospace design.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/standards/aerospace-material-specifications/385" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Gas Dynamics & Compressible Flow</div>
        <p>Study high-speed flows, shock waves, and their effects on aerospace vehicles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862342" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Aircraft Structures</div>
        <p>Understand structural design, analysis, and optimization for aerospace applications.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862350" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Spacecraft Systems</div>
        <p>Learn about subsystems for spacecraft including power, thermal, and attitude control.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862458" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Computational Fluid Dynamics</div>
        <p>Study numerical methods for analyzing fluid flow around aerospace vehicles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.102790" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Electric Propulsion</div>
        <p>Explore ion thrusters, Hall effect thrusters, and other electric propulsion technologies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.866173" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Avionics & Control Systems</div>
        <p>Master aerospace electronics, navigation systems, and flight control algorithms.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.868894" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Orbital Mechanics</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for analyzing spacecraft orbits, trajectories, and maneuvers.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862156" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Aircraft Safety & Certification</div>
        <p>Study certification processes, safety regulations, and airworthiness requirements.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.faa.gov/aircraft/air_cert/design_approvals/air_software/media/AC_20-115D.pdf" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Aerospace Manufacturing</div>
        <p>Understand production processes, quality control, and assembly techniques.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.103368" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Space Environment</div>
        <p>Explore radiation, microgravity, vacuum, and their effects on spacecraft design.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.nasa.gov/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nasa-std-3001-vol-2-rev-b.pdf" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Thermal Management</div>
        <p>Study heating issues and thermal protection systems for aircraft and spacecraft.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.862458" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Composite Structures</div>
        <p>Learn strategies for designing and analyzing composite materials in aerospace applications.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://arc.aiaa.org/doi/book/10.2514/4.103719" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

